a.n: One Day With - Kristina, Saint Petersbourg

p.k: This new episode of One day with presents the private life of one of the new Playboy TV Europe models: the Russian Kristina Muzhzhukhina! From the morning, enjoying her time in bed, until the evening, posing for a professional photographer in a motorhome. Kristina goes to the gym almost every day so she can keep her shape. Today we also accompany her on her first lesson of stand up paddle on a lake in Saint Petersburg. Although being a model, she loves to eat and to cook, and she shows us how to prepare the Viennese waffles. Kristina also loves to stroll naked at home and admire her own body in the mirror.
